{
  "stem": "8786.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He provided his family.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And even in the hardest times where Jewish children were not welcome in school-- I'm talking about the public school, or high school, or gymnasium-- all of-- all of his children did finished high school and even higher than that.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were strictly orthodox people, but education was on top of the list.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Even those very, very hard days I remembered that we were not welcome in the school, and he did not bargain on that.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "All of us did finish high school-- 1942, '43, and even 1944.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And this was already days where the anti-Semitism was [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] all over.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Everybody has effected, and it was in the school itself we were struggling, and felt very uncomfortable, and unwelcome.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I know it for a fact, that in my town for example-- it was a small town that I lived before the war.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The government made collections for-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] for winter clothing, which was supposed to send out for the American-- for the-- for the Hungarian army.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Naturally, in this small town, they did not have print shops.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So they came to the high school.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Will you please provide us with some beautiful signs.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Those few students who know how to make a nice sign-- have you going to put it out near the public places of the city.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "In the movie house, in the big-- in post office.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Wherever there was some-- naturally I was number one who was asked to do it, because I knew how to draw.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And as soon as I was finished with my beautiful sign, I took it in.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Next day, it was out in the biggest place but my name was covered up.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
